{"tid":2041233,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"好可能會不見天日 冇機會見到黎明(2)","createTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T06:29:16.000Z","uid":239516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"63584974facf7c52c756d29b318d77db9e6f95e7","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"依家既情況好唔樂觀 請你地好認真咁睇曬篇文佢<br />\n請你一定記得Be water, be humble 唔好睇得耐左就唔知佢真正既意義<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Be humble之少打飛機篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :</span><br />\n我先講5月24日既例子<br />\n相信長期出外抗爭既手足一定有發現<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然係係國安法既恐嚇下,5月24日遊行既人數仲係有唔少<br />\n但比以往既人數已經少左好多 當日遊行人數應該只有10至20萬左右<br />\n規模已經大減,行動亦相對好保守和平<br />\n見有熱門話因為大家去到都唔知可以點,亂曬咁走來走去<br />\n所以D狗都唔知點反應 (我唔知開post個位人兄有冇出去啦)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實佢地包圍網同之前一樣 仲要勁過之前<br />\n5月24日告士打道出面一早每個街口都放左大量警力<br />\n要包圍要收網 瘋狂捉人打人射人一早做到<br />\n其實係國安法消息一出,想試下水溫所以冇好似之前咁行動</span><br />\n所以個日我地付出既代價好細(受傷同被捕人數比較少)<br />\n係依到我想講既係唔好打咁多飛機啦 屌你老母臭系 傷身阿<br />\n面對現實了解下對方既行動 唔好嬴小小就打飛機 Be humble<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">國際與香港之關係篇:</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我們係國際上既回響係前所未有咁大 係因為國安法<br />\n其他國家亦唔至係得口交部回應,仲有實際行動<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">以前抗爭付出既代價咁大 但得換來其他國家既口交部回應<br />\n依家換來國安法 但絕對唔算係攬炒 更有可能比人一鋪清袋</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家先絕對係最危險既時候</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">巴打中國（最大贏家）精選留言:</span><br />\n認同依家係最危險，支那過左國安法，大家開心嘅位係令美國同好多國家出聲幫香港，<span style=\"color: violet;\">攬炒在望，但要記住外國係未有任何實際行動，一日未有實際行動，我地只係自炒緊</span>，所以依家香港人係要加多兩錢肉緊而唔係撓埋雙手等人救。<br />\n<br />\n外資唔走, 香港成為一國一制下可以運行既金融中心<br />\n一邊清算後生抗爭者 抗爭主力死亡 運動一定搞唔成<br />\n<br />\n外資本來就係仆街,得要搵錢 唔會理你香港人死活<br />\n依家係香港既美資一定會比壓力trump <br />\n叫佢step by step慢慢制裁<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">我們應保持抗爭加速/迫trump加大力度制裁</span>"},{"pid":"494855d5c03fc58fdd485c49224e12865d023d9b","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭力度及抗爭方向:</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國際會幫手, 但要你保持恆常既抗爭力度, 因為國安法一出, 國際既制裁, 絕對稱得上係出師有名。<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">巴打七加六精選留言:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即使再有大型勇武抗爭, 結果換黎都只會係畫面<br />\n實際做到既效果 不比和理非大很多</span><br />\n最多只係見多啲黑警受傷 建築物損壞<br />\n但對長遠 手足始終損失更多 承擔更大 更產生更大無力感<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">巴打神秘賓尼兔精選留言:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實我係驚有人會超級重視街頭抗爭當正係唯一抗爭手法</span><br />\n係依家呢個時勢係成本超高但效益唔顯著<br />\n不過點聚到人數但又避免圍捕都係一個難題<br />\n<br />\n依家D狗係國安法既加持下 唔洗再做門面功夫<br />\n遊行前封曬所有地區 分派係每個街口<br />\n封隧道查車 連著西裝/OL/咩人都查<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭成本低,回報高既時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以話係和理非時期<br />\n例如遊行集會保持一定人數, Twitter戰線日常化<br />\n屌你 姐係話勇武抗爭冇撚用啦?<br />\n唔係, 但視情況而出, 冇必要好似之前付出咁大代價</span>"},{"pid":"3e7a9d83afe067244fd8888efb72a3efbf02cd8c","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:05:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人移民篇:</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人話移民啦, 香港淪陷左架啦<br />\n首先唔係人人都有條件移民, 有人唔夠錢, 有人唔想走, 有人因為家庭, 所以唔係人人走到。<br />\n即使你移左民, 其實你要付出代價, 你要重新融入當地既社會(文化衝突,工作機會等等) <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">巴打浴火重生火鳳凰既精選留言:</span><br />\n佢指出移民要付出代價，例如後半世比白人嘅種族歧視，因為按照歷史進程，任何文明上嘅民主基本上都要由前人嘅艱苦努力、知識同鮮血換返嚟，台灣係咁，韓國係咁，歐美都係咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">你係喺度享受緊人地嘅民主成果，freerider 緊人地安逸嘅生活，而唔係去自己爭取返嚟，咁樣一定要付出代價</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唯有寄語比走嘅人可以繼續幫下香港，至少有多餘錢嘅可以幫下呢場革命，或者好似攬炒巴咁喺國際線上幫香港出聲，而唔係一走了之完全唔理香港，咁樣真係好人渣</span><br />\n<br />\n倒返轉 之前關係大個依家<br />\n因為要著重個點係美國郁鳩支那唔係基於國安法呢個原因"},{"pid":"5fecdece40daf3565ab941189d06fd859cc5c52f","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2nYbSs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2nYbSs.jpg&h=0b5f552f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea5bf0a9606a27aca2ad457e2d0817386ea6e76b","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKyc0LU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKyc0LU.png&h=a63173f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEBibSA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEBibSA.png&h=23b1bfbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4pzuEf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4pzuEf.jpg&h=fe3d167a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhhpRSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhhpRSB.jpg&h=68c04689&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yefVYxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyefVYxB.jpg&h=30fd46c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRArkLX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRArkLX.jpg&h=c84e1c80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c222f758531be30bded77dfbddf742a708150e8","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPsEFMd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPsEFMd.gif&h=f63c5995&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e17600fdfa0267386a85bf51712a34d27669dda1","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b27c964c5995cee4e14a888266d44fab88ff06","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e282b3a017b461207643873d802775b735cffdc2","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66069049aa8d4e40b5de9d82982249bb58e8014","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9cb84dae3d70bd8640c3001e791a003e0b0f06","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ceaa440faa01ef8d9a096ff2b65dc5dde4e3d9","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00776c90a436784320d6c57f5c0186261f756802","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e015c4d64aa6472cac29aa11f5c16c4f94299b","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917cb979d44354378fdba0e7d2f9196c49ec7678","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27564f9d27bc25930519ac69a88b18749b0fa82","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd89431acebda943ed7c83ab604ba8433846616","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c4275e974cf8d5808d36d679457aa5b770163","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a25efdc11c65172c8c767cde8609c21054b9c1d","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6761281aec74086336218b4aa96d679a6ad5d0","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf688216c0fc7c5a923107709a35497ae41f4e4","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b4e23dd3d06e135c51513fbca970213707ab98","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2163cf70b4e9804878d97743fcad21c567014ae0","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646735dc6f1db9cd75b6cf5c3bf7c371c7d474e7","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4a1f625004343b3a1a6235b4679d6fe667cfa0","tid":2041233,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}